### Buscar produtos
GET http://localhost:1337/api/products
?populate=image
&pagination[pageSize]=5
&pagination[page]=1
&filters[$or][0][title][$contains]=abc
&filters[$or][1][description][$contains]=descr

### Buscar categoria
GET http://localhost:1337/api/categories

### Login
POST http://localhost:1337/api/auth/local
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "identifier": "joao",
    "password": "123456"
}

### Criar usuário
POST http://localhost:1337/api/auth/local/register HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"username": "teste1",
    "email": "teste1@teste.com",
    "password": "123456"
}

### Listar itens do carrinho do usuário logado
GET http://localhost:1337/api/cart-items?populate[product][populate][image]=*
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6MSwiaWF0IjoxNzc0OTE5MjQ1LCJleHAiOjE3Nzc1MTEyNDV9.eV-F_IYeRLLW5lQKBoPEKCb2Xe7vwbv9cfzVddFRwek


### Adicionar Produto no Carrinho do usuário logado
POST http://localhost:1337/api/cart-items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6MSwiaWF0IjoxNzc0OTE4NDA0LCJleHAiOjE3Nzc1MTA0MDR9.OydCwBQwDm8bXaImLnbqSCB7DM0NystRV0w5ee0QLqE

{
	"data":{
		"quantity": 1,
		"product": "xgbh5qoow3whhlmp4incnjgk"
	}
}

### Atualizar Produto do carrinho
PUT http://localhost:1337/api/cart-items/hhte5hs0w56fvejuv9lpa2pw
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6NCwiaWF0IjoxNzc0Mzk0NTM3LCJleHAiOjE3NzY5ODY1Mzd9.NK0v9JiMElbQjgnASWiQe6hZVaJQr6s52dyxjgDfCWQ

{
	"data": {
        "quantity": 2
    }
}

### Deletar produto do carrinho
DELETE http://localhost:1337/api/cart-items/hhte5hs0w56fvejuv9lpa2pw
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6NCwiaWF0IjoxNzc0Mzk0NTM3LCJleHAiOjE3NzY5ODY1Mzd9.NK0v9JiMElbQjgnASWiQe6hZVaJQr6s52dyxjgDfCWQ
